{"about_the_game":"Sunburnt is a 2D, 1-bit arcade game where you avoid harsh rays of light that only seek your crispy demise. It features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fully 1-bit graphics<br></li><li>Tightly bound and remappable controls<br></li><li>Precise collisions with obstacles and allies alike<br></li><li>A special blend of calculated RNG and spices for unique plays with each attempt<br></li><li>12 semi-hidden achievements<br></li><li>All in a single game mode</li></ul><br><strong>A shaded oasis in the distance</strong><br><br>Desert sands with no end in sight; that is until, a jagged sign points you in the direction of salvation. Hope still remains...!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1244890/extras/animation1.png?t=1582876908\" /><br><br><strong>But it was just a moment's respite</strong><br><br>Relief from the sweltering heat lasts only a few seconds, before a daunting rustle in the leaves above makes you weary. An opening in the canopy lets forth a concentrated beam of blinding light and blistering heat. It doesn't look good, but at least you've bought yourself some time. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1244890/extras/animation2.png?t=1582876908\" /><br><br><strong>How long will you survive?</strong><br><br>Run, jump, and roll your way to safety in this 1-bit arcade. Various obstacles come your way, but know that there is a light at the end of the forest. Er, tunnel.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Wings of Wax","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1244890/12c171dd2b2b79ace2c97928f91d570b833f2692.jpg"},{"name":"Revelry in the Dark","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1244890/2f3357c571ff43c2a7affb9d39a557024be826b0.jpg"},{"name":"Hotfoot","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1244890/c0d90